OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780589464
OL,3,CWelsh Government ministers accused of
OL,4,Cclash of views in first FMQs
OL,6,FOpposition leaders in the Senedd have
OL,7,Faccused Welsh Government ministers of
OL,8,Fcontradicting each other when it comes
OL,9,Fto the NHS, nuclear power, and road
OL,10,Fbuilding here in Wales.
OL,12,FThe criticism came as Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,13,Ffaced his first question session in
OL,14,Fthe Senedd chamber since he became
OL,15,FFirst Minister last month.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
