FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780589464
OL,3,CWelsh Government ministers accused of
OL,4,Cclash of views in first FMQs
OL,6,FReform UK Wales leader, Dan Thomas,
OL,7,Fwho now leads the largest opposition
OL,8,Fparty, used his first three questions
OL,9,Fto highlight what he said was a clash
OL,10,Fof views within Plaid Cymru over
OL,11,Fdealing with the longest hospital
OL,12,Fwaiting lists.
OL,14,FTwo weeks ago, the new Welsh health
OL,15,Fminister, Mabon ap Gwynfor, told ITV
OL,16,FCymru Wales' Health Reporter Katie
OL,17,FFenton that he will make sure two-year
OL,18,Fwaits "are eliminated by the end of
OL,19,Four term".
OL,26,@{D@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780589464
OL,3,CWelsh Government ministers accused of
OL,4,Cclash of views in first FMQs
OL,6,FHowever speaking on ITV Cymru Wales'
OL,7,FThe Interviews programme, just weeks
OL,8,Fbefore the election, Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,9,Fsaid he expected "to be able to get
OL,10,Frid of those longest waiting times
OL,11,Fwithin a matter of months".
OL,13,FDan Thomas referred to that in his
OL,14,Fquestions, saying that, "During the
OL,15,Felection campaign, you said that two
OL,16,Fyear waits could end in a matter of
OL,17,Fmonths, but your new Health Minister
OL,18,Fhas said it will happen within four
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,26,@vD@YOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780589464
OL,3,CWelsh Government ministers accused of
OL,4,Cclash of views in first FMQs
OL,6,F"So my question is what expectations
OL,7,Fhas your government set for two year
OL,8,Fwaits? Is it the promise that you made
OL,9,Fduring the election campaign or is it
OL,10,Fwhat your health minister has said
OL,11,Fmore recently? And if it is the
OL,12,Flatter, will you apologise to voters
OL,13,Ffor misleading them during the
OL,14,Fcampaign?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780589464
OL,3,CWelsh Government ministers accused of
OL,4,Cclash of views in first FMQs
OL,6,FThe First Minster replied by saying
OL,7,Fthat "health is a priority here in
OL,8,FWales," and added that: "I made it
OL,9,Fvery, very clear that there are two
OL,10,Felements to what we are trying to do.
OL,11,FWe want to cut waiting lists in the
OL,12,Fshort term and we want to build a
OL,13,Fsustainable health and care service
OL,14,Ffor the long term.
OL,26,@oD@FOUpD@GO]pD@YOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780589464
OL,3,CWelsh Government ministers accused of
OL,4,Cclash of views in first FMQs
OL,6,F"I reiterate that a priority for us
OL,7,Fnow is to tackle in the coming months
OL,8,Fthose issues of the longest two year
OL,9,Fwaits, and in fact, I'm not waiting
OL,10,Ffor the next months. Work has already
OL,11,Fbegun to put in practice the changes
OL,12,Fthat are necessary to tackle that very
OL,13,Fissue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
